### 查询所有学院
GET http://localhost:8080/api/department

### 查询特定学院
GET http://localhost:8080/api/department/2

### 新增学院
POST http://localhost:8080/api/department
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "departmentId": 7,
    "departmentName": "测试学院"
}

### 批量新增学院
POST http://localhost:8080/api/department/batch
Content-Type: application/json

[
    {
        "departmentId": 8,
        "departmentName": "数学学院"
    },
    {
        "departmentId": 9,
        "departmentName": "外语学院"
    },
    {
        "departmentId": 10,
        "departmentName": "物理学院"
    }
]

### 修改学院
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/department
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "departmentId": 7,
    "departmentName": "试学院"
}

### 删除学院
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/department/7

### ========== 学生表 ==========

### 查询所有学生
GET http://localhost:8080/api/student

### 查询特定学生
GET http://localhost:8080/api/student/13

### 新增学生
POST http://localhost:8080/api/student
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "studentId": 11,
    "studentName": "张三丰",
    "departmentId": 1
}

### 修改学生
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/student
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "studentId": 11,
    "studentName": "张三丰(改名)",
    "departmentId": 1
}

### 删除学生
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/student/11

### 查询学生（带学院名称）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/student/withdept

### 查询单个学生（带学院名称）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/student/withdept/11

### 搜索学生（按姓名模糊查）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/student/search?studentName=张

### 搜索学生（按学院查）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/student/search?departmentId=1

### 搜索学生（姓名+学院组合查）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/student/search?studentName=张&departmentId=1

