### ========== 成绩表 ==========

### 查询所有成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/grade

### 分页查询所有成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/grade?page=1&size=5

### 查询特定成绩
GET http://localhost:8080/api/grade/1

### 新增成绩
POST http://localhost:8080/api/grade
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "studentId": 11,
    "courseId": 110,
    "grade": 95
}

### 修改成绩
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/grade
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gradeId": 1,
    "studentId": 11,
    "courseId": 110,
    "grade": 98
}

### 删除成绩
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/grade/1

### 搜索成绩（按学生ID查）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/grade/search?studentId=10

### 搜索成绩（按课程ID查）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/grade/search?courseId=110

